This is the directory for all YUI utilities.

The current util projects are:

* animation
* connection
* dragdrop
* dom
* event

Please observe the following pattern when checking in your projects:

yahoo/presentation/2.x/util/utilityname/
yahoo/presentation/2.x/util/utilityname/src
yahoo/presentation/2.x/util/utilityname/build
yahoo/presentation/2.x/util/utilityname/docs
yahoo/presentation/2.x/util/utilityname/examples